name: Self Portrait (While Switching Through Datagraphs) [Cryptoborg #7]
description:
'Sprawling beneath public cyberspace lies the labyrinthine underworld of the Datacombs [with their] ghost-stacks of sedimented virtuality, spiralling down abysmally into palaeodigital soft-chatter, through junk-programming, forgotten cryptoccultures, fossil-codes and dead-systems'.

Here you will find Zeta switching through the datagraphs of the Unscreened Matrix.
